---
title: Smoked Salmon Frittata Serves 2 | with Spinach and Chive Sour Cream
description: Elegance served on right out of the skillet! Smoked salmon, spinach, and tomatoes await with every bite of the delectable frittata! Chive Sourcream makes for the perfect savoury finish to this brunch dish.
